          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Assessing Barriers to Opioid Use Disorder Treatment Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to report on barriers to the provision of medication used to treat substance use disorders (e.g., buprenorphine) under Medicaid distribution models (e.g., provider purchasing, storage, and administration of medications). </p>]]></text>
